{"tid":2345701,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"婆婆在回收場坐著等，等變賣鋁罐舊報紙，但她不知道橫洲已被收村。","createTime":"2020-12-29T17:23:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-29T20:18:08.000Z","uid":78222,"like":28,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"bcd24352a460d3593730cb44f58f76aa30fa71c6","tid":2345701,"uid":78222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T17:23:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/CJYf2afg1m_/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCJYf2afg1m_%2F&d=WZfMoUUHHVTN90V%2FD%2BJOGVGN3hMT3pF%2B84p80JiLMiI%3D&h=a1b09af6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCJYf2afg1m_%2F&h=e1686541\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/CJYf2afg1m_/</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/permalink.php?story_fbid=733850257508601&amp;id=186269348933364&amp;__tn__=-R\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fpermalink.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D733850257508601%26id%3D186269348933364%26__tn__%3D-R&d=WZfMoUUHHVTN90V%2FD%2BJOGVGN3hMT3pF%2B84p80JiLMiI%3D&h=3b1eea3b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/permalink.php?story_fbid=733850257508601&amp;id=186269348933364&amp;__tn__=-R</a><br />\n<br />\n「婆婆！好熱呀！師傅（回收場負責人）未返，你要等好耐，下次先嚟過。」村民叫婆婆先回家，晚點再來。<br />\n婆婆沒有聽明白：<span class=\"gold\">「係呀！我等緊賣呢袋嘢（回收物）啊。」</span>婆婆拉著暗紅買菜車仔，滿半袋回收物，賣價應該不過5-10元。戴著卡其色漁夫帽，身穿桃紫色碎花上衣的她左顧右盼，想等師傅回來。她先找陰涼位站著，不到2分鐘，累了，找張廢紙墊屁股坐。<br />\n<br />\n       「婆婆，以後唔好嚟啦，你睇班工人都鋸樹拆屋，呢度（回收場）好快都冇㗎啦。」 <span class=\"gold\">婆婆聽著又忽爾點頭：「係呀。我嚟賣呢袋嘢㗎咋。」</span>曾在橫洲居住的村民趁著地盤未圍封之前想來看看舊家，拍照留念。他們勸婆婆回家，不要乾等。問出婆婆有個兒子，可是現在獨居，家裡有平安鐘，久不久就拿一袋車仔半滿的回收物變賣。<br />\n<br />\n............................................................<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"orange\">仲有兩段文字<br />\n我唔想全部copy曬<br />\n希望巴打入原link睇同share<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v2Yjn7n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv2Yjn7n.jpg&h=7380913f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nFB: 我不閱讀 <br />\nIG : idunread_bookstore"},{"pid":"a7da3fdf89ef7ce57a946484a8d4f6a86b2733ae","tid":2345701,"uid":78222,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T17:24:49.000Z","msg":"唔知可以做咩<br />\n但最起碼俾多啲人知呢件事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdc2fd2ba54a233ad0c31fb4f5b83e99e4680173","tid":2345701,"uid":54927,"like":3,"dislike":40,"score":-37,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T17:24:52.000Z","msg":"幾廿歲人搞成咁就反省下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8feff01fabfa3386ce736ccd5ce623ac3ddf2e57","tid":2345701,"uid":8600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T17:25:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5b95e124beb836df614a9bb1dd669a1f195f0902","tid":2345701,"uid":78222,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"quote":{"pid":"cdc2fd2ba54a233ad0c31fb4f5b83e99e4680173","tid":2345701,"uid":54927,"like":3,"dislike":40,"score":-37,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T17:24:52.000Z","msg":"幾廿歲人搞成咁就反省下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T17:26:30.000Z","msg":"講得啱呀 政府反省下啦<br />\n淨係識賣港清洗香港人<br />\n屌佢老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33de240f2c2fe6aa50d79f061024098fe923d5ab","tid":2345701,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T17:27:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"766384ac097c387b5833bc2af07c808c539f2403","tid":2345701,"uid":78222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T17:28:09.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28db89b3afe84d345e9b9c418b0955b1a901765f","tid":2345701,"uid":54927,"like":2,"